      "rationale": "Inlet flow rate, rotational speed, fluid viscosity, and density were sourced from calibrated instrumentation (±2% flow, ±0.5 RPM) and ASTM F1841 fluid property tables. Boundary condition documentation is archived in the project technical file. Pediatric operating conditions (lower flow rates) were defined by clinical protocol but no corresponding CFD input sensitivity study was performed for the expanded range."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
