      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; sample provenance documented.",
      "rationale": "Porcine blood samples used in the 2023 in-vitro campaign were sourced from a licensed abattoir, prepared within 6 hours of collection, and characterized for hematocrit and plasma hemoglobin prior to each test run. Sample documentation is retained in the laboratory notebook. Formal test-sample adequacy assessment not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
