      "rationale": "For each of the five adult validation operating points, CFD inlet velocity profiles, rotational speed, and fluid properties were set to match the in-vitro measurements within the stated instrumentation uncertainty bands. Equivalency was confirmed by overlaying CFD and experimental pressure-flow curves. Equivalency assessment was not extended to pediatric operating conditions because no in-vitro pediatric test runs were conducted; the team considered the adult equivalency demonstration transferable to the expanded envelope without additional verification."
